---
// Pie tipo telemetría analógica (decorativo).
---

<footer class="telemetry about-reveal" aria-hidden="true">
    <span>SIGNAL ▰▰▰▰▰▰▱</span>
    <span>NTSC · 60Hz</span>
    <span>ON AIR SINCE 2022</span>
</footer>

<style>
    .telemetry {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: clamp(0.6rem, 0.58rem + 0.2vw, 0.72rem);
        letter-spacing: 0.22em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--c-dim);
        border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
        padding-top: 1rem;
    }
    .telemetry span:first-child {
        color: var(--c-blood);
    }
</style>
